    "记录页面跳转与关键操作（已自动脱敏，不含账号、Cookie 等敏感信息），日志按大小滚动并自动清理。日志文件也可在「文件」App → 我的 iPhone/iPad → Han1meViewer → Logs 中找到，遇到问题时可导出并附到 GitHub issue。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Records screen navigation and key actions (already redacted — no account, cookies, or other sensitive info). The log rolls over by size and is pruned automatically. You can also find the log file in the Files app → On My iPhone/iPad → Han1meViewer → Logs and export it to attach to a GitHub issue."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "记录页面跳转与关键操作（已自动脱敏，不含账号、Cookie 等敏感信息），日志按大小滚动并自动清理。日志文件也可在「文件」App → 我的 iPhone/iPad → Han1meViewer → Logs 中找到，遇到问题时可导出并附到 GitHub issue。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "記錄頁面跳轉與關鍵操作（已自動去識別化，不含帳號、Cookie 等敏感資訊），日誌依大小滾動並自動清理。日誌檔案也可在「檔案」App → 我的 iPhone/iPad → Han1meViewer → Logs 中找到，遇到問題時可匯出並附到 GitHub issue。"
          }
        }
      }
